tarted back in 6th grade with simple game programming, and that initial spark has grown into a deep passion for Systems and Networking Development. I love the challenge of designing, building, and optimizing the core infrastructure that powers our digital world.\nMy primary focus is on crafting robust networking protocols and distributed systems. I dive deep into specifications (like the various RFCs for DNS) to build tools like Drasil-DNS, a Rust-based library aiming to be part of a larger, self-hostable DNS resolver. I also enjoy exploring the intricacies of operating systems, which led me to create Catalyst-OS, a learning project built from scratch in Rust.\nWhile systems are my core interest, I believe in broad exploration. You'll find projects in my portfolio spanning Full-Stack web development (using stacks like MERN and Django) and even AI-powered tools like Oratio, which transforms research papers into audio podcasts using self-hosted models. I thrive on learning new technologies and applying them to solve interesting problems.\nFeel free to explore my projects, check out my code on GitHub, or reach out if you'd like to discuss technology, potential collaborations, or exciting opportunities!\n","description":"","id":"http://127.0.0.1:1111/about/","path":"/about/","title":"About Me"},"http://127.0.0.1:1111/posts/":{"body":"","description":"","id":"http://127.0.0.1:1111/posts/","path":"/posts/","title":"Posts"},"http://127.0.0.1:1111/projects/":{"body":"","description":"","id":"http://127.0.0.1:1111/projects/","path":"/projects/","title":"Projects"},"http://127.0.0.1:1111/projects/drasil/":{"body":"","description":"Rust based DNS packet serializer and deserializer library","id":"http://127.0.0.1:1111/projects/drasil/","path":"/projects/drasil/","title":"Drasil"},"http://127.0.0.1:1111/projects/freighter/":{"body":"","description":"A simple but extensible load balancer written in Go-lang","id":"http://127.0.0.1:1111/projects/freighter/","path":"/projects/freighter/","title":"Freighter"},"http://127.0.0.1:1111/projects/lambent/":{"body":"","description":"A interpreted programming language inspired by Lambda Calculus","id":"http://127.0.0.1:1111/projects/lambent/","path":"/projects/lambent/","title":"Lambent"},"http://127.0.0.1:1111/projects/lucerna/":{"body":"","description":"Research Paper discovery and Podcast Generation platform","id":"http://127.0.0.1:1111/projects/lucerna/","path":"/projects/lucerna/","title":"Lucerna"},"http://127.0.0.1:1111/projects/mosaicify/":{"body":"","description":"Mosaicify is a Photo Gallery and sharing app built as our project for the PISC (PICT IEEE Student Chapter) organised Hackathon - Tech Rush","id":"http://127.0.0.1:1111/projects/mosaicify/","path":"/projects/mosaicify/","title":"Mosaicify"}},"docInfo":{"http://127.0.0.1:1111/":{"body":42,"description":0,"path":0,"title":2},"http://127.0.0.1:1111/about/":{"body":145,"description":0,"path":0,"title":0},"http://127.0.0.1:1111/posts/":{"body":0,"description":0,"path":1,"title":1},"http://127.0.0.1:1111/projects/":{"body":0,"description":0,"path":1,"title":1},"http://127.0.0.1:1111/projects/drasil/":{"body":0,"description":7,"path":2,"title":1},"http://127.0.0.1:1111/projects/freighter/":{"body":0,"description":7,"path":2,"title":1},"http://127.0.0.1:1111/projects/lambent/":{"body":0,"description":6,"path":2,"title":1},"http://127.0.0.1:1111/projects/lucerna/":{"body":0,"description":6,"path":2,"title":1},"http://127.0.0.1:1111/projects/mosaicify/":{"body":0,"description":16,"path":2,"title":1}},"length":9},"lang":"English"}